The paper deals with the problem of synchronizing rankings through interactive communication, which involves information editing and different constraints on communication throughput. This problem is relevant to several areas of computer science, including information theory (cs.IT), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), distributed computing (cs.DC), social and information networks (cs.SI), and machine learning (cs.LG). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
